{"tid":1838752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢的肺炎傳過來，傳過來，傳過來","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:03:55.000Z","uid":52658,"like":65,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"aceadf2f8bfdd56ea47b61f78f13fb4138b1d0ca","tid":1838752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:40:40.000Z","msg":"武漢的肺炎傳過來<br />\n傳過來 傳過來<br />\n這裡的病院很精采<br />\n請不要假裝不理不睬<br />\n<br />\n武漢的肺炎傳過來<br />\n傳過來 傳過來<br />\n不要被沙士名字嚇壞 其實它很可愛<br />\n<br />\n我左看右看 上看下看 <br />\n原來每個病人都不簡單 <br />\n我想了又想 我猜了又猜 <br />\n武漢的感染人數 還真奇怪 <br />\n<br />\n真奇怪啦啦啦啦 啦啦啦啦啦<br />\n啦啦啦啦啦啦啦 噢欸噢<br />\n<br />\n公眾場所的蒼蠅拍 <br />\n左拍拍 右拍拍 <br />\n為甚麼還是沒人要來<br />\n無人問津 真無奈 <br />\n<br />\n武漢的肺炎傳過來<br />\n到北京 到上海<br />\n寂寞病人肺炎初開 需要你給我一點藥<br />\n<br />\n武漢的肺炎不要來<br />\n到台灣 到香港<br />\n不要試著逃出武漢<br />\n相信黨 信祖國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n任賢齊到武漢舉辦倒數演唱會 為孝順父親順道帶同父親回武漢探親<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1808089\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1808089</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"371d390d7f5efef1faeed08f66dbb40d27a462fc","tid":1838752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e9e68bb494376e6ded3a356b4a09ed7a6b895a","tid":1838752,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e829914cc1415c5b64a514e7eff3db1e90909b","tid":1838752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971d439c52a6ebcce2bcf6b4e2db4a35c89e6191","tid":1838752,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p